history.content:
Hi Samir, 

The sections are all exactly the same, just at different time. I would check HKN.eecs.berkeley.edu or check the old websites for these courses.

Our current website for 61A is cs61a.org --> note that since class is currently in session, we releasing assignments on our own timeline. However, you can kind of follow along! You can also check old websites like Nicole mentioned below.

---

You can't really choose a section too well before classes start since you won't know which TA teaches each section, but for 61a and 8, all the TAs are great. I would choose based on location and timing. Which can you make since you really do want to go section. If you want to change it up later, you might be able to, but switching might have changed as enrollment has increased.

Our current website for 61A is cs61a.org --> note that since class is currently in session, we releasing assignments on our own timeline. However, you can kind of follow along! You can also check old websites like Nicole mentioned below.

Hi My name is Samir Naqvi, and I am going to take CS C8 and 61A in the fall, and am looking for someone who can advise me on which sections to take, and someone who if possible could send me the lectures and labs (incomplete of course), so that I can go through the class during summer to prepare myself.
